-- Turcas, Socar Get Regulator Approval for Petkim Refinery in Western Turkey
-- Mark Bentley
-- 2010-06-24T10:52:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-24/turcas-socar-get-regulator-approval-for-petkim-refinery-in-western-turkey.html

          
          
             The State Oil Company of the
Azerbaijan Republic and Turkey’s Turcas Petrol AS, got regulator
approval for unit Petkim Petrokimya Holding AS to build a
refinery in western Turkey.  
 The approval for the license of 49 years was published on
the Web site of Turkey’s energy regulator, Turcas said in a
filing with the Istanbul Stock Exchange today.  
          
          


  


        